  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/8bd0b44ef7af776fec1184e900d6a3da.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We need to print tickets for customers and prepare their orders. The best way to ensure satisfied customers is with fast and complete service!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/8b2599eafa470ebbf8795b7a07a8f396.poster.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/8b2599eafa470ebbf8795b7a07a8f396.webm?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/8b2599eafa470ebbf8795b7a07a8f396.mp4?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/3923cbbff7ed5a48bc00cb29c3aaf07c.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To provide uninterrupted service to customers, we must continuously restock our supplies as they run out. Remember, the more products you have, the more sales you make.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/aa5761049f9fee12db1c1891dc3bc041.poster.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/aa5761049f9fee12db1c1891dc3bc041.webm?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/aa5761049f9fee12db1c1891dc3bc041.mp4?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/c3dcb2cf0bbe8b94cd1c6d217765c9c6.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >License films and set the playback order of showtimes. The film scheduling system, the most detailed system in the game, offers you many opportunities to develop strategies. You can either set high prices and show popular films or sell to more people at a lower price. You can try many combinations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/e3d846a01010e3f45af3f88aace15b77.poster.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/e3d846a01010e3f45af3f88aace15b77.webm?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/e3d846a01010e3f45af3f88aace15b77.mp4?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/e922b7376e5e916b245883cf2e09a05e.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By purchasing new items for your cinema, you can gain more storage space, visual appeal, and functionality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/a6abdbc19de66be8aa9cb97f6f7badbc.poster.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/a6abdbc19de66be8aa9cb97f6f7badbc.webm?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/a6abdbc19de66be8aa9cb97f6f7badbc.mp4?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/8bd0b44ef7af776fec1184e900d6a3da.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We need to print tickets for customers and prepare their orders. The best way to ensure satisfied customers is with fast and complete service!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/8b2599eafa470ebbf8795b7a07a8f396.poster.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/8b2599eafa470ebbf8795b7a07a8f396.webm?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/8b2599eafa470ebbf8795b7a07a8f396.mp4?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/3923cbbff7ed5a48bc00cb29c3aaf07c.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To provide uninterrupted service to customers, we must continuously restock our supplies as they run out. Remember, the more products you have, the more sales you make.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/aa5761049f9fee12db1c1891dc3bc041.poster.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/aa5761049f9fee12db1c1891dc3bc041.webm?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/aa5761049f9fee12db1c1891dc3bc041.mp4?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/c3dcb2cf0bbe8b94cd1c6d217765c9c6.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >License films and set the playback order of showtimes. The film scheduling system, the most detailed system in the game, offers you many opportunities to develop strategies. You can either set high prices and show popular films or sell to more people at a lower price. You can try many combinations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/e3d846a01010e3f45af3f88aace15b77.poster.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/e3d846a01010e3f45af3f88aace15b77.webm?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/e3d846a01010e3f45af3f88aace15b77.mp4?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/e922b7376e5e916b245883cf2e09a05e.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By purchasing new items for your cinema, you can gain more storage space, visual appeal, and functionality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/a6abdbc19de66be8aa9cb97f6f7badbc.poster.avif?t=1743188373\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/a6abdbc19de66be8aa9cb97f6f7badbc.webm?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327470/extras/a6abdbc19de66be8aa9cb97f6f7badbc.mp4?t=1743188373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
